title: Coinbase Expects Spot Bitcoin ETFs to Add Billions to Crypto Market — Says SEC Approval Possible by Year-End
description: Cryptocurrency exchange Coinbase says spot bitcoin exchange-traded funds (ETFs) could add billions of dollars to the total crypto market cap. Coinbase also believes that the chances of one or more spot bitcoin ETFs being approved by the U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) before the end of 4Q23 “have sharply improved.” Coinbase’s Spot Bitcoin ETF […]

title: Africa Tech Summit Partners with Raenest for its Sixth Edition in Nairobi
